synthesis models and pre-main sequence tracks. This analysis serves\nas a testbed of our technique to constrain the low-mass IMF in young super-star\nclusters as well as an exploration of the star formation history of young UC\nHII regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2010 18:08:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
