-Newtonian terms relevant for the microarcsecond accuracy is\nelucidated. We demonstrate that these terms result from an inadequate choice of\nthe impact parameter in the standard post-Newtonian formulas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2010 11:48:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Feb 2010 17:00:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
